fulltitle: Insiders' Response to the Warren Report
title: Insiders' Response to the Warren Report
description:
Mr. Thompson conducted one the investigations into the Kennedy assassination that disagreed with the Warren Commission Report, including the development of the “two bullets” theory. He said the Zapruder tape is still open to multiple interpretations. After his presentation he answered audience members' questions. 

Mr. Thompson is a private investigator and the author of, Six Seconds in Dallas.

*David Talbot*
Editor-in-Chief
Salon.com

*Josiah Thompson*
Private Investigator
